<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Daily Inspiration</title>
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: "Segoe UI", Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b, #334155);
      color: #f8fafc;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .card {
      max-width: 800px;
      width: 100%;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 30px;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.35);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
    }
    h1 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 2rem;
      color: #facc15;
    }
    blockquote {
      margin: 18px 0;
      padding-left: 16px;
      border-left: 4px solid #38bdf8;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #e2e8f0;
    }
    .author {
      text-align: right;
      color: #93c5fd;
      font-style: italic;
      margin-top: -8px;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #cbd5e1;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 8px;
      padding: 6px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.2);
      border: 1px solid rgba(56, 189, 248, 0.4);
      color: #bae6fd;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <h1>🌟 Daily Inspiration</h1>

    <blockquote>
      “Success is the sum of small efforts, repeated day in and day out.”
    </blockquote>
    <div class="author">— Robert Collier</div>

    <blockquote>
      “Discipline is choosing between what you want now and what you want most.”
    </blockquote>
    <div class="author">— Abraham Lincoln (attributed)</div>

    <blockquote>
      “The expert in anything was once a beginner.”
    </blockquote>
    <div class="author">— Helen Hayes</div>

    <div class="footer">
      Keep learning. Keep building. Keep shipping. 🚀<br />
      <span class="tag">Powered by Harish's Docker Web Server</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
